00:17:57,777 --> 00:18:00,062
Congratulations.

511
00:18:01,164 --> 00:18:03,131
Thank you.

512
00:18:03,166 --> 00:18:04,916
Anything else?

513
00:18:04,951 --> 00:18:06,451
No.

514
00:18:09,172 --> 00:18:11,006
Actually, yes.
Oh, yeah?

515
00:18:11,040 --> 00:18:13,491
Would you like some tips
on the best bar in Mykonos?

516
00:18:13,509 --> 00:18:15,677
Or maybe we could play
some Lady Gaga trivia.

517
00:18:15,711 --> 00:18:18,046
Or perhaps you're looking for
some tips on how to remove

518
00:18:18,097 --> 00:18:20,015
Merlot stains
out of skinny jeans?

519
00:18:20,049 --> 00:18:22,667
